data.description: Welcome to Summerwood Life & Living! Enjoy this Spacious 4-6 Bedroom/ 3 Full Bath/2 Car Garage home, that Boasts of  Beautiful Art Niches, Arched Entryways, Vaulted Ceilings, Neutral Tones, Tile/Wood Flooring Through-out, Open Concept Kitchen and a Covered Back Porch Patio with Retractable Shades & Recent Ceiling Fans. This Well-Maintained Beauty has NO CARPET in the home! All Tile, and Wood Flooring throughout. (2) Added Bonus Flex Rooms in this home, make this one a Special Rare Find! Either Flex Room can be used as a Gym, Nursery, Media Room, Office, or whatever you'd like. Wheelchair Accessible accommodations with Oversized Doorways, and Security Rails in bathroom.  Must see to Truly Appreciate all of the Beauty this Rare Gem has to Offer. Easy access to Beltway 8. Minutes away from Retail, Dining, Parks, Health, Wellness & Fitness. Zoned to Highly Desired Humble ISD!!
